OL,3,CSleeping skipper to pay #10,000 for
OL,4,Ccausing fishing boat crash
OL,6,FThe crash was caught on camera by
OL,7,FMuscle Fishing. The two men on board
OL,8,FBlackbird can be heard shouting and
OL,9,Fwaving before saying "we have to get
OL,10,Fout of the way" and "brace" before the
OL,11,Fimpact.
OL,13,FAt Lewes Crown Court, Reid pleaded
OL,14,Fguilty to failing to do what was
OL,15,Frequired as master to prevent his ship
OL,16,Ffrom causing serious damage to another
OL,17,Fship or serious injury to another
OL,18,Fperson, under Section 58 of the
OL,19,FMerchant Shipping Act 1995.
