OL,4,Ccausing fishing boat crash
OL,6,FReid also pleaded guilty to failing to
OL,7,Fmaintain a proper look out, under the
OL,8,FMerchant Shipping (Distress Signals
OL,9,Fand Prevention of Collisions)
OL,10,FRegulations 1996.
OL,12,FReid was sentenced to eight months
OL,13,Fimprisonment, suspended for 12 months.
OL,15,FHe was also ordered to complete 100
OL,16,Fhours of unpaid work and pay #10,000
OL,17,Fin costs.
