OL,6,FFollowing the sentencing MCA
OL,7,Finvestigator Martin Hayward said:
OL,8,F"This was a dangerous situation caused
OL,9,Fby the master of the fishing vessel
OL,10,Ffailing to adhere to the collision
OL,11,Favoidance rules, which could have had
OL,12,Fdisastrous consequences were it not
OL,13,Ffor the quick thinking of those on the
OL,14,Fvessel in danger. The outcome could
OL,15,Fhave been much worse.
OL,17,F"The UK fishing industry has the
OL,18,Fhighest proportion of deaths and
OL,19,Fserious injury per capita of any
OL,20,Findustry within the UK.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
