OL,4,Ccausing fishing boat crash
OL,6,F"Many events involving casualties on
OL,7,Ffishing vessels are a result of
OL,8,Fcomplacency, neglect and flagrant
OL,9,Fdisregard for the law.
OL,11,F"This is unacceptable and those
OL,12,Ffishers and owners who put lives at
OL,13,Frisk will be prosecuted.
OL,15,F"The MCA continues to work with the
OL,16,Ffishing industry to improve safety,
OL,17,Fand those not willing to engage,
OL,18,Fimprove levels of compliance and
OL,19,Foperate safely will face the full
OL,20,Fweight of the law."
